{"tid":2002791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇老懵董呢個中國第一大愛國者?","createTime":"2020-05-05T11:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T13:52:44.000Z","uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"298176ae5379c3d286aca6fe759bf0794367f2e8","tid":2002791,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"二世祖一名，賣哂老豆家業，正常人收哂錢應該出走，但佢仍然留係香港。<br />\n<br />\n你話佢愛國我覺得錯唔哂，但我覺得佢仲似大陸共產黨擁護者。即係後者＞前者。貪污點錯都好， 共產黨政權係無錯"},{"pid":"d77bc8917170256397177b180c8cd70662e2917f","tid":2002791,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"我地90後覺得有啲野錯就係錯，但係佢果代啲人好似覺得錯既唔代表任何野。<br />\n<br />\n而共產黨錯太多，就算佢想做一啲野改變，始終改變唔到"},{"pid":"39f464f8fcd110dd58dbdaa2f2b4acb6dd90f1f1","tid":2002791,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"你點知佢唔走唔係因為有把柄喺人手上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1517ca2a0c2f67b2820deb4816446bc414ed6b7","tid":2002791,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"腳痛落台呢種奇恥大辱我諗佢到死都唔會釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔洗do又有雞毛舞吓滿足個人囉"},{"pid":"558f8220b42728506796cab9f2689700586c5866","tid":2002791,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f464f8fcd110dd58dbdaa2f2b4acb6dd90f1f1","tid":2002791,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"你點知佢唔走唔係因為有把柄喺人手上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"但係大陸肯用幾百億收佢間公司，你唔理政治，中央點都唔搞你。真係夠你食幾代，呢一代大魚大肉都仲有1~2百億"},{"pid":"cd4939fa41a7b61e31381af4861962abc393843d","tid":2002791,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1517ca2a0c2f67b2820deb4816446bc414ed6b7","tid":2002791,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"腳痛落台呢種奇恥大辱我諗佢到死都唔會釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔洗do又有雞毛舞吓滿足個人囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"可能做開二世祖，未做過一件驚天大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想搞少少野名留青史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05a2a8234291d47ca4fc87be04f757e9d1453c4","tid":2002791,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}